<div class='media__message'>
<h4 class='h12 talk-link__speaker'>매트 케니언</h4>
<h4 class='h9 m5'>
<a class='' href='http://www.ted.com/talks/matt_kenyon_how_i_snuck_a_memorial_for_iraqi_civilians_into_the_us_government?language=ko' lang='ko'>
나는 어떻게 US정부에 이라크 시민들에 대한 추모를 끼워 넣었는가
</a>
</h4>
<div class='meta'>
<span class='meta__item'>
Posted
<span class='meta__val'>
Aug 2015
</span>
</span>
<span class='meta__row'>
Rated
<span class='meta__val'>
Courageous, Ingenious
</span>
</span>
</div>
